StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetOrganiza.onTypes]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
select organiza.on_type as Organiza.onType, short_descrip.on as ShortDescrip.on from mcriss.dbo.organiza.on_type FOR XML PATH('OrgType'), ROOT('Organiza.onTypes')
